data.description:
Well maintained home, walking distance to the lake on dead end street in Sheffield Lake, 4 bedroom colonial, one bedroom on first floor,
three bedrooms on second floor. New carpet in family room, white washed wood burning fireplace, new double oven in kitchen, new
"closets by design "pantry and storage in kitchen. Full bathroom new vinyl flooring and vanity. Deck with built in fireplace, two car
attached garage, vinyl siding, leaf gutters, new roof and windows. All appliances stay, including washer and dryer, custom blinds on all
windows stay. Garage cameras and video doorbell stay
